{"title":"减租谣","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"减租谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏人家地，头顶人家天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佃户千千万，辈辈受熬煎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕种又收割，四季忙不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食刚进囤，车马到门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主提大斗，收租把眼翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簸箕簸，扇车扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交了租，粮食完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥里水里干一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄米颗颗不见面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄上好清闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赌罢钱来抽大烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃酒内，穿绸缎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃穿那儿来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是佃户的血和汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×  ×  ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从来了共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佃户生活得改善，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种地的团结一股劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减租斗争大开展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到如今，吃的饱，穿的暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组织互助搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导佃户把身翻。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}